<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.3.6">
<l>kalliṉ munnīr māṟṟi vantu kāval kaṭantilaṅkai</l>
<l>yallal ceytā ṉuṅkaḷ kōmā ṉemmai yamarkkaḷattu</l>
<l>vella killā tañci ṉōṅkāṇ veṅkati rōṉciṟuvā,</l>
<l>kolla vēṇṭā vāṭu kiṉṟōm kuḻama ṇitūramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Your king, having come altering the three-watered [sea] with boulders,</l>
<l>Overcoming the defenses in Laṅkā,</l>
<l rend="indent">created misfortune for us on the battlefield.</l>
<l>Being unable to subdue [him], we were terrified. Look!</l>
<l>Child of the hot-rayed [sun], do not kill us.</l>
<l rend="indent">We are dancing to the kuḻamaṇitūram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
